EAGLE: ^"Well, well, well... What do we have here? A little fire-breather causing trouble in my territory."
^"Unhand me, you overgrown feather duster! You don't know who you're dealing with."
^"Oh, I know exactly who you are, Felix. And I know what you can do. That's why "Boss Morbius" wants your power for himself."
^"Boss Morbius? What does he want with me?"
^"He wants to harness your fire-breathing ability to spread darkness across Foxhaven. And I'm here to make sure you don't cause any more trouble."
^"You'll never get away with this! I'll burn you to a crisp!"
^"We'll see about that. But for now, you're coming with me."
